{"word":"ἄμ","slug":"ἄμ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n4844\" key=\"a)/m\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἄμ</orth>, for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀνά,</foreign> before words beginning with <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">β</itype>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">π</itype>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">φ</itype>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">μ</itype>, e.g. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἂμ βωμοῖσι, ἂμ μέσον, ἂμ πεδίον, ἂμ πέλαγος, ἂμ φυτά;</foreign> also compds., as <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀμπαύω</foreign>:—mostly <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Dor.\">Dor.</a></gram></gramGrp>, as in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pi.\">Pi.</a></author></bibl>, but also in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author></bibl>, sts. in Trag.</entryFree>"}]}